---
import { Card } from '@/components/Card';
import { CardContainer } from '@/components/CardContainer';
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout title='Testimonials'>
  <h1>Customer Testimonials</h1>

  <div class='featured-image-container'>
    <img
      src='/images/browndogbiscuits-20240102_110332-2975647146.jpg'
      alt='Happy dogs enjoying our treats'
      class='featured-image'
    />
    <p class='image-caption'>
      What our furry friends and their humans have to say about Brown Dog
      Biscuits
    </p>
  </div>

  <CardContainer className='basic-card-grid'>
    <Card className='basic-card testimonial-card' title='Corey & Marta'>
      <div slot='content'>
        <div class='rating'>★★★★★</div>
        Maple absolutely loves the peanut butter treats! They are the perfect size
        for training, and I love knowing they are made with natural ingredients.
        We are customers for life!
      </div>
    </Card>
    <Card className='basic-card testimonial-card' title='Tom & Bella'>
      <div slot='content'>
        <div class='rating'>★★★★★</div>
        "The variety of flavors keeps things interesting for Charlie. He especially
        loves the blueberry treats. Thank you for making such high-quality products!"
      </div>
    </Card>
    <Card className='basic-card testimonial-card' title='Maria & Rocky'>
      <div slot='content'>
        <div class='rating'>★★★★★</div>
        "Our pup has never been so excited for treats! These are clearly made with
        love and care."
      </div>
    </Card>
    <Card className='basic-card testimonial-card' title='David & Luna'>
      <div slot='content'>
        <div class='rating'>★★★★★</div>
        Luna gets so excited when she sees the Brown Dog Biscuits bag. Best treats
        we have ever found!
      </div>
    </Card>
    <Card className='basic-card testimonial-card' title='Jennifer & Cooper'>
      <div slot='content'>
        <div class='rating'>★★★★★</div>
        Cooper is usually picky with treats, but he absolutely loves these. Great
        quality!
      </div>
    </Card>
    <Card className='basic-card testimonial-card' title='Mike & Bailey'>
      <div slot='content'>
        <div class='rating'>★★★★★</div>
        "We love supporting local businesses, especially when they make such amazing
        products!"
      </div>
    </Card>
    <Card className='basic-card testimonial-card' title='Lisa & Charlie'>
      <div slot='content'>
        <div class='rating'>★★★★★</div>
        "These treats are perfect! Charlie sits by the treat jar waiting for his
        daily Brown Dog Biscuit."
      </div>
    </Card>
    <Card className='basic-card testimonial-card' title='Amanda & Zeus'>
      <div slot='content'>
        <div class='rating'>★★★★★</div>
        "Zeus gives these treats two paws up! We love the all-natural ingredients."
      </div>
    </Card>
  </CardContainer>

  <div class='cta-container'>
    <p>Would you like to share your experience?</p>
    <a href='/contact.html' class='cta-button'>Contact Us</a>
  </div>
</ContentLayout>

<style>
  .rating {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
